RESTful API written in Scala, using the Play Framework.

To start the application:
    ./activator run

And then http://localhost:9000

To use the REST API:
	curl -X POST http://localhost:9000/create -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "{\"name\": \"John\"}"
	curl -X GET http://localhost:9000/users/1
	curl -X GET http://localhost:9000/users 
